column5: What is that mean? Always seeing member mention it.  Thanks in advance
OOS - out of season Is that what you were wondering?
Soon we will be viewing photos of OOS Musky because it is not against the board rules, Ontario regs or unethical. I can't wait.
What about the famous WGSF   . Maybe I'll do some PIKE fishing in Pigeon lake this weekend and have a photo or two for you kickingfrog    .
WGSF = Worlds Greatest Sport Fish = Rock Bass  I wonder what you thought it stood for?
And here I wuz thinking it was about bass from the Nederlands.  JF
Those photes should not be on this site , who agrees?
OOS Stands for Oh Okay Sure (Im "pike" fishing)
